Aviva Drops Daniels From Chairman Shortlist, Independent Reports

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-03-20T20:32:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/aviva-drops-daniels-from-chairman-shortlist-independent-reports.html
Eric Daniels, the former chief
executive officer of  Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY) , will be removed
tomorrow from the shortlist of those being considered for the
position of chairman of insurance company  Aviva Plc (AV/)  after some
investors protested against his being included among the
candidates for the position, the Independent reported without
saying where it got the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Simpson at 
 jsimpson12@bloomberg.net  